name: Pasan y pasan
description:
Video taken with an iphone X on 5/20/20 from the bike path in a little park at Pachuca, Hidalgo, Mexico. Edited on Glitché app on the same date. 

+ just an attempt from a young man to savour a moment and then create an aesthetic experience from it for him to share.
